{"tid":2104144,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"倒垃圾青年重拾書本　發奮圖強終獲哈佛取錄","createTime":"2020-07-11T17:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T14:12:18.000Z","uid":306109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4551145045d0d3bab15d02cd32f7470c6e0baccc","tid":2104144,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"史塔頓當時的同事全部是<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">釋囚</span></span></strong>，他們都認為史塔頓不應屈就於倒垃圾公司，鼓勵他再報考大學。他指那是他一生中首次獲人真心鼓勵。同事們最終與垃圾收集公司老闆的兒子貝斯（Brent Bates）商討，並將史塔頓介紹予包伊州立大學（Bowie State University）的教授。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200711/bkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200711%2Fbkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=298bf8ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200711/bkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n仗義每多屠狗輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0bc1f34f5f52d256578512a063ddb7d623f47a","tid":2104144,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"白粉就出全文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國馬里蘭州一名命途多舛的青年，高中畢業後為了家計，就職垃圾收集員。但他在同事鼓勵下毅然重拾書本，一邊倒垃圾賺學費、一邊到大學上課，如今畢業更獲哈佛大學法學院取錄，取得珍貴進修機會。<br />\n現年24歲的史塔頓（Rehan Staton）在8歲時被拋棄，與身兼母職的父親相依為命，家境貧困。史塔頓高中時曾志願成為職業拳擊手，惟天意弄人，肩膊受傷後運動員夢碎。他臨時趕報大學，卻未獲取錄，輾轉成為了垃圾收集員。<br />\n史塔頓當時的同事全部是釋囚，他們都認為史塔頓不應屈就於倒垃圾公司，鼓勵他再報考大學。他指那是他一生中首次獲人真心鼓勵。同事們最終與垃圾收集公司老闆的兒子貝斯（Brent Bates）商討，並將史塔頓介紹予包伊州立大學（Bowie State University）的教授。<br />\n最終，史塔頓獲該校取錄，更考得優異成績，轉往馬里蘭大學。他於前年畢業後成為政治顧問公司的分析員，同時應付法學院考試，最終成功考入哈佛大學，未來將專攻運動法律。"},{"pid":"687ffbca7c2ed2a3cca49c9b3a9227e5edbbf28e","tid":2104144,"uid":325263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4551145045d0d3bab15d02cd32f7470c6e0baccc","tid":2104144,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"史塔頓當時的同事全部是<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">釋囚</span></span></strong>，他們都認為史塔頓不應屈就於倒垃圾公司，鼓勵他再報考大學。他指那是他一生中首次獲人真心鼓勵。同事們最終與垃圾收集公司老闆的兒子貝斯（Brent Bates）商討，並將史塔頓介紹予包伊州立大學（Bowie State University）的教授。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200711/bkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200711%2Fbkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=298bf8ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200711/bkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n仗義每多屠狗輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T00:47:59.000Z","msg":"關仗義咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778e287f25cfed06ed92b4b8975611d4be6c5890","tid":2104144,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"687ffbca7c2ed2a3cca49c9b3a9227e5edbbf28e","tid":2104144,"uid":325263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4551145045d0d3bab15d02cd32f7470c6e0baccc","tid":2104144,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"史塔頓當時的同事全部是<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">釋囚</span></span></strong>，他們都認為史塔頓不應屈就於倒垃圾公司，鼓勵他再報考大學。他指那是他一生中首次獲人真心鼓勵。同事們最終與垃圾收集公司老闆的兒子貝斯（Brent Bates）商討，並將史塔頓介紹予包伊州立大學（Bowie State University）的教授。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200711/bkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200711%2Fbkn-20200711070116966-0711_00972_001.html&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnvG%